'''GoVenture''' is the [[brand name]] for a series of [[educational computer game]]s and [[simulation]]s developed and published by MediaSpark Inc. The first GoVenture simulation was launched in 2000 and several more have been launched since. GoVenture educational games and simulations are themed on [[business]] and [[money]] subjects and are designed to give learners realistic experiences with various [[business process]]es and financial topics.{{Citation needed|date=August 2011}}
