'''The Marketing Institute of Ireland''' (MII) is the professional body for [[Republic of Ireland|Ireland]]'s marketing people,<ref>{{Cite web|title = The Marketing Institute Golf Society|url = http://www.migs.ie/history.php|website = www.migs.ie|accessdate = 2015-09-22}}</ref> in operation since 1962.<ref>{{Cite web|title = About Us - Marketing Institute of Ireland|url = https://mii.ie/about-us/|accessdate = 2015-09-24}}</ref> The Marketing Institute provides training courses and organises the All Ireland Marketing Awards (AIM Awards)<ref>{{Cite web|title = All Ireland Marketing Awards|url = http://aimawards.ie/about.htm|website = aimawards.ie|accessdate = 2015-09-22}}</ref> and digital marketing event, DMX [[Dublin]].<ref>{{Cite web|title = About - DMX 2015|url = http://www.dmxdublin.com/about/|accessdate = 2015-09-22}}</ref>

== Events ==
The All Ireland Marketing Awards (AIM Awards), was established by The Marketing Institute in 2007. This event recognises the success of Irish marketing<ref>{{Cite web|title = RTÉ Digital Receive Two AIM Award Nominations {{!}} RTÉ Digital Blog|url = http://digitalblog.rte.ie/2014/03/06/rte-digital-receive-two-aim-award-nominations/|website = digitalblog.rte.ie|accessdate = 2015-09-24}}</ref> - with 19 categories ranging from marketing campaigns to best teams.<ref>{{Cite web|title = All Ireland Marketing Awards 2015 - Small Business Can|url = http://www.smallbusinesscan.com/event/all-ireland-marketing-awards-2015/|accessdate = 2015-09-22}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.irishtimes.com/business/media-and-marketing/why-women-are-driving-the-marketing-sector-1.585743|title = Why women are driving the marketing sector|date = 2015-09-25|accessdate = |website = The Irish Times|publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.herald.ie/news/tomorrow-is-the-deadline-for-the-marketing-institutes-2015-allireland-marketing-awards-the-awards-cover-marketing-campaigns-across-as-many-as-18-categories-including-new-product-top-ad-campaign-and-the-marketing-team-of-the-year-entries-can-be-made-online-at-wwwaimawardsie-30962224.html|title = The Herald|date = 2015-09-25|accessdate = |website = Tomorrow is the deadline for the Marketing Institute's 2015 All-Ireland Marketing awards|publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref>

DMX Dublin is a digital marketing event,<ref>{{Cite web|title = Want to know the secrets of digital marketing for SMEs?|url = http://businessetc.thejournal.ie/dmx-dublin-sme-stream-1316343-Feb2014/|accessdate = 2015-09-24|first = Susan|last = Daly}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = DMX Dublin 2015|url = http://irishtechnews.net/ITN3/dmx-dublin-2015/|website = irishtechnews.net|accessdate = 2015-09-24}}</ref> with over 30<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.herald.ie/news/city-to-host-international-experts-in-new-media-at-dmx-digital-conference-30962221.html|title = The Herald|date = |accessdate = |website = City to host international experts in new media at dmx digital conference|publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref> international and local speakers in 4 presentation streams, and 800 marketing professional attendees.<ref>{{Cite web|title = About - DMX 2015|url = http://www.dmxdublin.com/about/|accessdate = 2015-09-22}}</ref>

== Education programmes ==
The Marketing Institute offers one and two-day workshops, as well as intensive training programmes - MSc in Digital Marketing and Analytics<ref>{{Cite web|title = MSc Digital Marketing & Analytics - The Marketing Institute|url = https://mii.ie/course/digital-masters/|accessdate = 2015-09-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.irishtimes.com/business/media-and-marketing/making-the-most-of-data-firms-collect-1.1844916|title = Making the most of data firms collect|date = 2015-09-24|accessdate = |website = The Irish Times|publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref> and The&nbsp;Postgraduate Diploma in Management and Marketing.

Both programmes are operated by the Marketing Institute of Ireland in partnership with [[Dublin Institute of Technology|Dublin Institute of Technology (DIT)]]. The MSc in [[Digital marketing|Digital Marketing]] and Analytics is an executive master's degree.<ref>{{Cite web|title = Dublin Digital Marketing Training Courses 2014 - Gaumina Digital Agency - we always offer ongoing digital advice|url = http://www.gaumina.ie/irish-digital-marketing-courses-2014-2/|accessdate = 2015-09-24}}</ref> The&nbsp;Postgraduate Diploma in Management and Marketing&nbsp;is a Level 9 one-year part-time conversion course for graduates from&nbsp;non-business disciplines.<ref>{{Cite web|title = Management & Marketing for Non-Business Graduates - Conversion Programme {{!}} postgradireland.com – course information and advice for students in Ireland and Northern Ireland|url = http://postgradireland.com/course/11228|website = postgradireland.com|accessdate = 2015-09-24}}</ref>

